Getting Started
===============

Running The Game
----------------

$ python game_player.py -l LARCENYBIN -g GAMEFILE

(Example on CCIS Linux)

$ python game_player.py -l /usr/bin/larceny -g /course/cs4500wc/Assignments/Game10/game.sps.slfasl


(Example with random seed)

$ python game_player.py -g /course/cs4500wc/Assignments/Game10/game.sps.slfasl -s 675434126 -q 879542811


Command Line Options
--------------------

        -i    Outputs small amount of informational output to a logfile

        -d    Outputs *large* amount of debugging information to a logfile

        -l    Path to Larceny program

        -g    Path to game file

        -s    First seed variable

        -q    Second seed variable


